title: A Blind Teabagging Fiasco (2009), Deep Fried Sack Dreams (2010),
description:
**Re-uploaded since I don't know why I can't seed my own torrent**

Since the mixtape scene seems to be dying out a 
bit I have decided to release one last tape to 
show everyone my skill in throwing together 
scenes from stuff ranging from 1 second to a 
little over a minute. This tape contains a 
whopping 196 scenes squeezed in 1 hr and 13 
minutes with intro and credits. 

This is my private project strictly animation, 
cartoons, and other material all hand drawn. 
No computer generated animation footage was used.

Expect to see:

* Extreme Hentai
* Funny cartoon scenes from my childhood.
* Crazy brutal animation.
* Funny splicing moments.
* Other stuff

{*Disclaimer:*}
The Producer of this film would like to dedicate
this film to Mike, Kevin, and Ryan who helped with
film ideas on my two previous projects.

I would also like to thank Grandpa Fucking Spaceshuttle
whose mixtape was so bad I had to make a more 
entertaining one.

This Film contains scenes of extreme amine rape, silly
cartoon moments, and flash toons I found interesting
when browsing the internet.


I also uploaded my first and second mixtape in case 
some people want to download them and check em out.
Our first tape was kind of brutal, second was
funny and this last tape I made is a great mix.
